OL,4,G2030FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GToilet troubles, tossing and
OL,6,     Gturning, and tears galore. It's a
OL,7,     Grip-roaring payment day on Four
OL,8,     Gin a Bed. But who's won the week?
OL,9,G2100F24 Hours in A&E
OL,10,     GLewis, who's 18, has come off his
OL,11,     Gmotorbike and collided with two
OL,12,     Gcars. Sam, who's 27, fainted and
OL,13,     Gcut his lip while smoking a Cuban
OL,14,     Gcigar at a barbecue.
OL,15,G2200F24 Hours in A&E
OL,16,     GEmma, who's 47, needs a CT scan
OL,17,     Gfollowing a bike crash with a
OL,18,     Gbus. Josh, who's 33, has severe
OL,19,     Gback pain. Pamela, who's 87, is
OL,20,     Gworried that she may have a blood
OL,21,     Gclot in her leg.
